{"id": "1492810328105549915", "channel_id": "1492810328105549915", "type": 0, "author_id": "667315390912921621", "author_name": "that_one_chippy", "author_bot": false, "content": "我記得前陣子看過這種藝術風潮。而且我真的很想把它畫出來！我認為這很適合杜勒赛因和西维斯特，除了顯而易見的吃人這一點之外。我認為這是一個既脆弱又有深意的概念。\n\n我希望能透過我的藝術作品傳達更深層的意義！🐈 (我盡力做了一個心形的……)\n注意：我並非最初的潮流引領者！這個點子不是我原創的，我只是用這些角色重新繪製罷了！", "timestamp": "2026-04-12T08:55:17.295000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-12T09:25:49.534000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "doresain_proud", "emoji_id": "1468257815238938645", "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1492810329065783336", "filename": "dfsf.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1935769, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1492810328105549915/1492810329065783336/dfsf.png?ex=69dcaf75&is=69db5df5&hm=3e700413a6e46a155d5f87a97a4f9c95c0d7727cef9ac96926c75536782a59ac&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1492810328105549915", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我的心，獻給你 || 杜勒赛因x西维斯特", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537"]}
